               </p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="186112160047"></xptr>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Flicker was further charged with having been before convicted.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18611216-name-124" type="witnessName">
