                        <interp inst="t18611216-name-124" type="surname" value="TUCKER"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18611216-name-124" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN TUCKER</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Policeman, E</hi> 168). I produce a certificate—(<hi rend="italic">This certified the conviction of Thomas Flicker, on his own confession, at the Westminster Police Court, in March, of larceny.—
Confined Six Months</hi>)—the prisoner is the person to whom that applies—I was present when he was convicted.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">GUILTY</hi>.**—<hi rend="italic">
